    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you\u2019d think this beauty just rolled off the showroom floor today\u2014it\u2019s been pampered like crazy and kept tucked away in a garage. The interior still has that fresh smell, the paint is flawless, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look or ask any questions. You seriously won't find another one this clean!",
