    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in absolute showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark, stone chip, or blemish, having been professionally ceramic coated and kept in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather seats are supple and free of creases, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service folder documenting every oil change and inspection performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives exactly as it did the day it was manufactured\u2014tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of machinery for the discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
